en:
Yes!
Definitely in my top three for sure!

You have NO idea how many emotional
rollercoasters I've been on with those kinds
of books.

Do I regret it?
<s>Not one bit of course!!!</s>

It's always very interesting to see how
different characters handle different
situations.

After all, these genres teach us about
peoples' many emotions and perspectives
the most.

That's why these genres are my second
favorite!
